data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT!! Motivated sellers!! Spacious and beautiful!! Come and see this 4 bed, 2 full bath home in the heart of Independence. Newer HV/AC, water heater, and roof. This home is charming with beautiful hardwoods throughout.  The main level has a 4th bedroom, which could also be used as an office. As soon as you walk into the family room, you will notice the spacious area and lovely fireplace. The large kitchen is especially stunning with a fireplace, large sliding glass doors that lead out to the backyard area, a large island perfect for preparing meals, and even comes equipped with a separate prep sink! There is also a full bathroom downstairs. Upstairs is just as impressive with a large primary bedroom with two closets, 2 additional bedrooms, and a full bath.  There is a sub-basement area with plenty of storage space as well. This home truly has it all! THE SELLER IS ALSO WILLING TO PARTICIPATE IN RATE BUY-DOWN OPTIONS!!!  Buyer/buyer agent to verify all information.
